title: Indian Lake Shores
description: In-law style apartment in a lake community.  10 minutes from URI and beaches.  Heat, hot water and electricity included.￼  Swimming, fishing, kayaking on lake.  First and security.

title: 2 bedroom townhouse SK
description: 2 bedroom townhouse with garage. Spacious bedrooms 10x20 and 10x14 with extra large closets. The first level is an open floor plan with private deck facing the woods.( close to URI and the bike path). The condo has central air and gas heat. There is an attached garage as well. Updated washer and dryer as well as newer hot water heater.
No pets no smoking. Tenant pays utilities.

title: Charming c:1880 Renovated Cape in South Kingstown
description: Located between off 108 just North of PeaceDale on a quiet dead end street. Charming c:1820 duplex with 880 sq ft living space, 1 bedroom, 1 1/2 baths, and lots of natural light. New Windows ready to be installed. New furnace, Updated Electric, Exterior walls doubled with additional 2x4 insulated walls.New roof. Realtor owned and marketed. Tenant pays own utilities, year round only.
